---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Architectural Model Making Services | Carve Model"
  description="Full-service architectural model making: scale models, sales-gallery models, product prototypes, topographic models, and film miniatures. Turnkey from scope to delivery, serving the U.S. and Canada."
  canonicalPath="/scale-model-services"
  ogTitle="Architectural Model Making Services | Carve Model"
  ogDescription="Scale models, sales-gallery models, product prototypes, and film miniatures — built turnkey, in-house."
  active="services"
  imageSlot={true}
>
<Fragment slot="head">
<script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={`{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Service","serviceType":"Architectural model making","provider":{"@type":"ProfessionalService","name":"Carve Model","areaServed":["United States","Canada"]},"hasOfferCatalog":{"@type":"OfferCatalog","name":"Model making services","itemListElement":[{"@type":"Offer","itemOffered":{"@type":"Service","name":"Architectural Scale Models"}},{"@type":"Offer","itemOffered":{"@type":"Service","name":"Sales Gallery & Presentation Models"}},{"@type":"Offer","itemOffered":{"@type":"Service","name":"Product Prototypes"}},{"@type":"Offer","itemOffered":{"@type":"Service","name":"Film & Commercial Miniatures"}},{"@type":"Offer","itemOffered":{"@type":"Service","name":"Art Installations & Sculpture"}}]}}`} />
<style>
.page-hero{padding-top:clamp(3rem,6vw,5rem);padding-bottom:clamp(2.5rem,4vw,4rem);border-bottom:1px solid var(--cm-line-faint);}
.page-hero h1{margin-top:1.4rem;}
.page-hero p{margin-top:1.4rem;}
.svc-block{display:grid;grid-template-columns:0.9fr 1.1fr;gap:clamp(2rem,4vw,4rem);align-items:center;padding-block:clamp(3rem,5vw,5rem);border-bottom:1px solid var(--cm-line-faint);}
.svc-block:nth-child(even) .svc-block__media{order:-1;}
.svc-block__media image-slot{width:100%;aspect-ratio:4/3;}
.svc-block h2{font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.6rem);letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-top:1.1rem;}
.svc-block p{margin-top:1.1rem;color:var(--cm-gray-300);}
.svc-block ul{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:1.6rem 0 0;display:grid;gap:0.7rem;}
.svc-block li{display:flex;gap:0.7rem;align-items:flex-start;font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--cm-text-muted);}
.svc-block li svg{flex:none;margin-top:4px;color:var(--cm-silver);}
@media(max-width:820px){.svc-block{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.svc-block:nth-child(even) .svc-block__media{order:0;}}
</style>
</Fragment>

<main>
<section class="page-hero"><div class="container">
  <span class="eyebrow">Services</span>
  <h1 class="display-lg measure">Full-service model making, managed in-house.</h1>
  <p class="lead measure">We provide custom physical model making supporting architectural design, product development, and film previsualization — a turnkey process covering scope, engineering, fabrication, finishing, and logistics.</p>
</div></section>

<div class="container">
  <article class="svc-block" id="architectural">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">01 — Architecture</span>
      <h2>Architectural Scale Models</h2>
      <p>From simplified block models for early design to detailed replicas highlighting façade, materials, glazing, and structure. Built for planning approvals, stakeholder presentations, investor meetings, and sales galleries.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Massing &amp; concept models for entitlement and planning reviews</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Detailed presentation models for clients and public exhibitions</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Large-scale models for multi-building developments — massing, circulation, site</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-block__media"><image-slot id="svc-arch" placeholder="Drop architectural model photo"></image-slot></div>
  </article>

  <article class="svc-block" id="sales">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">02 — Marketing</span>
      <h2>Sales Gallery &amp; Presentation Models</h2>
      <p>High-finish display models designed to make a strong visual impression. Detailed finishes, lighting options, and premium presentation bases for marketing suites and investment pitches.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Lit models with integrated LED and acrylic detailing</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Premium bases, vitrines, and branded plinths</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Built to anchor sales centers and launch environments</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-block__media"><image-slot id="svc-sales" placeholder="Drop sales gallery model photo"></image-slot></div>
  </article>

  <article class="svc-block" id="product">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">03 — Product</span>
      <h2>Product Prototypes</h2>
      <p>We support product designers and engineers by transforming sketches and CAD files into fully built physical mockups — for design validation, demos, and investor conversations.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> CAD-to-physical mockups for hardware startups</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Appearance and form-study models</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Finish, material, and scale exploration</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-block__media"><image-slot id="svc-product" placeholder="Drop product prototype photo"></image-slot></div>
  </article>

  <article class="svc-block" id="film">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">04 — Film</span>
      <h2>Film &amp; Commercial Miniatures</h2>
      <p>We work closely with art departments to design and fabricate miniature sets for previsualization and cinematic planning. Crafted from lightweight, film-grade materials, ready for transport or on-location staging.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Previsualization sets for cinematic planning</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Commercial &amp; product miniatures</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Lightweight, location-ready builds</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-block__media"><image-slot id="svc-film" placeholder="Drop film miniature photo"></image-slot></div>
  </article>

  <article class="svc-block" id="topographic">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">05 — Site</span>
      <h2>Topographic &amp; Site Models</h2>
      <p>Accurate representations of terrain, hardscape, and landscape — roads, water features, and grade changes. Ideal for planning, design reviews, and wayfinding studies.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Contour terrain and grade modeling</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Landscape, roads, and water features</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Context massing for surrounding sites</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-block__media"><image-slot id="svc-topo" placeholder="Drop topographic model photo"></image-slot></div>
  </article>

  <article class="svc-block" id="art" style="border-bottom:0;">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">06 — Art</span>
      <h2>Art Installations &amp; Sculpture</h2>
      <p>We collaborate with artists, designers, and cultural institutions to fabricate sculptural works and installation pieces — translating a concept or maquette into a precise, durable, exhibition-ready object.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Maquette-to-final fabrication and scaling-up</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Mixed-material builds for gallery &amp; public display</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M3 8.5l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg> Mounting, finishing, and install-ready delivery</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-block__media"><image-slot id="svc-art" placeholder="Drop art installation / sculpture photo"></image-slot></div>
  </article>
</div>

<section class="section"><div class="container">
  <div class="cta reveal" style="position:relative;text-align:center;background:var(--cm-black);border:1px solid var(--cm-border);border-radius:var(--r-sm);padding:clamp(3rem,6vw,5rem) var(--gutter);">
    <h2 class="display-md">Not sure which model you need?</h2>
    <p class="muted mt-2" style="max-width:46ch;margin-inline:auto;">The right first step is understanding what decision your model needs to support. Tell us about your project and we'll recommend the scope.</p>
    <div class="mt-4" style="display:flex;gap:0.9rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;"><a class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" href="/contact">Get a Free Quote →</a><a class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg" href="/model-making-process">See our process</a></div>
  </div>
</div></section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
